		/// <param name="flGreen">If the <i>iMode</i> parameter is PAL_BITFIELDS, the <i>flRed</i>, <i>flGreen</i> and <i>flBlue</i> parameters are masks that show which bits correspond to red, green, and blue. Each mask must consist of contiguous bits and should not overlap other masks. All combinations of bitfields are supported by GDI.</param>
		/// <param name="flBlue">If the <i>iMode</i> parameter is PAL_BITFIELDS, the <i>flRed</i>, <i>flGreen</i> and <i>flBlue</i> parameters are masks that show which bits correspond to red, green, and blue. Each mask must consist of contiguous bits and should not overlap other masks. All combinations of bitfields are supported by GDI.</param>
